  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to evaluate the ability of fluid responsiveness by stroke volume
      variation value of NICOM(Noninvasive cardiac output monitor)system during congenital cardiac
      surgery.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
